Function Reference/get the content feed « WordPress Codex
-----------

Retrieve the post content for feeds.

Usage
-----

` <?php get_the_content_feed( $feed_type ); ?> `

Parameters
----------

 `$feed_type` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) The type of feed. Can be: rss, rss2, atom or rdf.
    Default: null

Return Values
-------------

 `` `(string)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   The filtered content.

Change Log
----------

Since: [2.9](/Version_2.9 "Version 2.9")

Source File
-----------

`get_the_content_feed()` is located in `wp-includes/feed.php`

